<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Worship takes many forms, some formal, some less. I grew up in a Baptist church, which was pretty informal, but I <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>always</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> had the sense that it was reverent. Does that make any sense? <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
