When I see that some churches only take a cursory look/attitude into these 'events', it really bothers me. I don't want to overemphasize the nature of baptism, or the Last Supper, or laying on of hands, etc., but too often in my experience, they have been underemphasized.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
