<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>So within two years the congregations celebrated the Lord's Supper at every service. In the process people learned the value, joy, awesome-ness of this &quot;event.&quot; Public worship without the Lord's Supper seemed incomplete. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
